examples.en: The admiral gave the signal of recall.
The admiral had been declared faultless.
The admiral edged away with his squadron.
examples.ru: Адмирал начал незаметно отодвигать свою эскадру.

examples.en: I reported myself to the admiral, and joined my brig.
examples.ru: Я доложил о себе адмиралу и взошёл на бриг.
